OL,3,CPause inheritance tax changes for
OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,FA committee of MPs has called on the
OL,7,FUK Government to pause changes to
OL,8,Finheritance tax rules until the
OL,9,Fspecific impact on Welsh farmers has
OL,10,Fbeen examined.
OL,12,FThe cross-bench Welsh Affairs Select
OL,13,FCommittee, which is made up of a
OL,14,Fmajority of Labour MPs, has accused
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer's government of
OL,16,Fhaving a "complacent approach", and
OL,17,Fcreating an "unnecessary climate of
OL,18,Fconfusion about the possible impact of
OL,19,Fthe changes".
