OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,FDuring an interview with ITV News in
OL,7,FSeptember, the Prime Minister said his
OL,8,Fproposed reforms, which will see
OL,9,Fagricultural assets worth more than
OL,10,F#1million taxed at 20%, will take
OL,11,Feffect in April 2026 despite
OL,12,Fopposition from farmers.
