OL,3,CPause inheritance tax changes for
OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Treasury said:
OL,7,F"Right now 40% of Agricultural
OL,8,FProperty Relief ` worth #219m - goes
OL,9,Fto just 117 estates. Our reforms will
OL,10,Fchannel that funding into vital public
OL,11,Fservices. We're backing British farms
OL,12,Fwith #1million Annual Investment
OL,13,FAllowance for plant and machinery
OL,14,Finvestments, billions for sustainable
OL,15,Ffood, and action to cut EU export
OL,16,Fcosts".
