OL,3,CPause inheritance tax changes for
OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,FThe Welsh Affairs Committee's report
OL,7,Fdoes not hold back with its concerns
OL,8,Fabout the changes, not just for
OL,9,Findividual farmers affected, but the
OL,10,Findustry as a whole in Wales.
OL,12,FThe parliamentary committee argues the
OL,13,Fchanges to inheritance tax could have
OL,14,Fa disproportionate impact on Welsh
OL,15,Ffarmers, due to the unique nature of
OL,16,Fthe industry here. The report notes
OL,17,Fthat the majority of farms in Wales
OL,18,Fare small family-run livestock
OL,19,Fbusinesses, with an average income of
OL,20,Faround #22,000.
