OL,3,CPause inheritance tax changes for
OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,FAt the heart of the committee's
OL,7,Fconcern is the lack of official data
OL,8,Fassessing the policy's impact on Welsh
OL,9,Ffarmers. The report highlights what it
OL,10,Fcalls an "information vacuum", which
OL,11,Fhas been filled by different
OL,12,Forganisations publishing competing
OL,13,Fstatistics which suggest vastly
OL,14,Fdifferent estimates.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
