OL,3,CPause inheritance tax changes for
OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,FThe UK Government has said most
OL,7,Festates will not be affected by the
OL,8,Fchanges. On the government webpage
OL,9,Fexplaining the policy, it says:
OL,10,F"Reforms to agricultural property
OL,11,Frelief are expected to affect the
OL,12,Fwealthiest 500 estates each year with
OL,13,Fsmaller farms not affected by the
OL,14,Fchanges. So that means almost three-
OL,15,Fquarters of estates claiming
OL,16,Fagricultural property relief,
OL,17,Fincluding those that also claim for
OL,18,Fbusiness property relief, would not be
OL,19,Faffected by the changes, based on the
OL,20,Flatest available data."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
