OL,3,CPause inheritance tax changes for
OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,FBut the Welsh Affairs Committee says
OL,7,Fthat data is not good enough.
OL,8,FCommittee chair Ruth Jones MP said the
OL,9,Fway her party has introduced
OL,10,Finheritance tax changes has been
OL,11,F"complacent", particularly following
OL,12,Fthe amount of public anger towards the
OL,13,Fpolicy.
OL,15,FHowever, the Newport and Islywn Labour
OL,16,FMP said she agreed with the need to
OL,17,Freform inheritance tax, and described
OL,18,Fher committee's intervention as "not a
OL,19,Fstop and end it, just a stop and think
OL,20,Fplease".
