OL,3,CPause inheritance tax changes for
OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,FAsked how people in the industry are
OL,7,Ffeeling about the impending changes to
OL,8,Fthe tax rules, she said: "I would say
OL,9,Fa range from disappointed and
OL,10,Fconcerned to absolutely terrified. I
OL,11,Fthink what annoys people, particularly
OL,12,Fmyself included, is how unfair it
OL,13,Ffeels."
OL,15,FThe committee says the change in
OL,16,Fpolicy may have a disproportionate
OL,17,Fimpact on elderly farmers or those
OL,18,Fwith terminal illness who have
OL,19,Farranged their affairs on the basis
OL,20,Fthat their estates would not be
OL,21,Fsubject to inheritance tax.
