OL,3,CPause inheritance tax changes for
OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,F"My grandfather bought our farm in
OL,7,FJune 1950," Kath said. "He paid #1,860
OL,8,Ffor it".
OL,10,FIt's worth 10 times that now but she
OL,11,Fsays it's not necessarily producing
OL,12,Fany more value due to the price of
OL,13,Fland.
OL,15,F"In retrospect we would have made
OL,16,Fchanges before, but there was no need
OL,17,Fto do it then."
