OL,3,CPause inheritance tax changes for
OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,FKath fears the impact the changes
OL,7,Fwould have on younger farmers. She
OL,8,Fsays if they lose hope at the thought
OL,9,Fof large tax bills every time a
OL,10,Ffarming generation passes on the land
OL,11,Fand machinery, some may consider
OL,12,Fleaving the industry.
OL,14,F"If you lose a farm, it doesn't come
OL,15,Fback," Kath said. "And if we lose a
OL,16,Fgeneration of farmers now, it's not
OL,17,Fgoing to come back. And where's our
OL,18,Ffood security then?"
