OL,3,CPause inheritance tax changes for
OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,FIn a warning to the UK Government, the
OL,7,FWelsh Affairs Committee report
OL,8,Fconcludes that a failure to account
OL,9,Ffor the unique role farming plays in
OL,10,FWales risks undermining the viability
OL,11,Fof rural farming communities, the
OL,12,FWelsh language, and the future of
OL,13,Ffarming in Wales.
