OL,3,CPause inheritance tax changes for
OL,4,Cfarmers, Welsh MPs tell UK Government
OL,6,FIn addition to its calls to delay
OL,7,Finheritance tax reforms, the report
OL,8,Fmakes recommendations relating to
OL,9,Fagricultural funding, the challenges
OL,10,Fand opportunities for the Welsh
OL,11,Ffarming industry presented by recent
OL,12,Ftrade agreements and how best to
OL,13,Fsupport and secure the next generation
OL,14,Fof Welsh farmers.
